      "page_number": 1,
      "raw_text": "The pittsburg Land and Improve\nment company, which is planning a\nnew addition to the city at the north\nend of Monroe street to be known as\nMonroe Park, expects to have its sur\nveying and plating done this week\nThe plat will be fled at once and street\ngrading started at the earliest possible\nmoment. Little work will be required\nto shape up the streets as the land\nis level and the soil gravel.\n\n\nThe lots will be placed on the market\nat once and will be handled by sew\neral local real estate men, at several\npoints in the Palouse country, and in\nPittsburg in the east."
    }
